# Set userToken/adminToken via ManualSecurityTest before running these calls

### Populate guides and trips
GET {{url}}/trips/populate

### Get all trips (requires USER or ADMIN)
GET {{url}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Get trips filtered by category (e.g., beach)
GET {{url}}/trips?category=beach
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Get a trip by id (includes guide + packing list)
GET {{url}}/trips/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Create a new trip
POST {{url}}/trips
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "startTime": "2024-08-01",
  "endTime": "2024-08-05",
  "locationCoordinates": 55.67,
  "category": "CITY",
  "price": 2500
}

### Update an existing trip
PUT {{url}}/trips/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "tripId": 1,
  "startTime": "2024-08-02",
  "endTime": "2024-08-06",
  "locationCoordinates": 57.00,
  "category": "CITY",
  "tripPrice": 2700
}

### Delete a trip
DELETE {{url}}/trips/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Link guide to trip (use ADMIN token if you prefer)
PUT {{url}}/trips/4/guides/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get guide totals
GET {{url}}/trips/guides/totalprice
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
